name: Down
description:
What used to be light becomes dark
Cornered without light
I lost my sight
Blind to the future

What used to be free becomes constrained
Cornered without power
I lost my way
Legs don't even want to move

What used to be dynamic becomes static
Cornered, not moving

I forgot about the sun
I forgot about the stars
My world lost day and night
There is only darkness
Dimming all hope

I can watch
But can't avoid the decision
If I fall
I won't let the light go out
I will put my feet on the pillar of hope
Until I'm still able to rise again
